---
title: Sweet Chilli Glazed Veggie Gyozas with Hoisin Spring Greens Udon Stir-Fry
description: Our Sweet Chilli Glazed Veggie Gyozas is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
